Sensor data

Data formatting function

Columns :
- index number of the measure,
- date and time in UTC,
- time zone = 4 (French Guiana is UTC-3)
- T1, T2, T3,
- soil moisture count,
- shake = 0
- errFlag (if =1 the device couldnt convert time from PCF chip) = NA
